{"word":"ἀπολούω","slug":"ἀπολούω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀπολούω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:λούω\">λούω</a></el>; the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> ‘wash’] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <el>ἀπολούομαι</el>, ‘remove personal defilement’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> non-specific use <b><i>wash oneself</i> <a href='B:530 6:11'>1 Cor 6:11</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of sins, with intensive aspect of <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a></el> <b><i>wash off, wash away</i> <a href='B:510 22:16'>Ac 22:16</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπολοῦμαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀπολύτρωσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}